CNS Inc said it completed itsinitial public offering of 1,035,000 shares of common stock at3.75 dlrs a share through an underwriting group headed byEngler-Budd and Co Inc.    Concurrent with the offering, the company made an exchangeoffer in which it issued 277,127 common shares in exchange for935,333 dlrs of outstanding promissory notes at the rate of3.375 dlrs a share. This represented over a 93 pct acceptanceof the exchange offer, the company said. Reuter&#3;